<HEADLINE>
INFLATING THE COST OF 'FREE AIR' 
</HEADLINE>
 COL-AZR   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By DAVID LEIBOWITZ   
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
