</P>
<P>
   A0904 BC-TIMBER-INJUNCTION-COX 499 22:56 U A
</P>
<P>
   A0902 BC-IMMIG-ASYLUM-NYT 594 22:52 U A
</P>
<P>
   ASYLUM WON BY GHANAIAN WOMAN WHO FEARED MUTILATION &QL;
