   MINOR-COLUMN _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ Bad news, ladies and
gentlemen. The airlines _ those good folks who delay your flight
when the plane's not full and then leave your luggage behind _ have
been fiddling around with your derriere. What I mean, specifically,
is that if you have to fly somewhere _ say to a convention in
Topeka next May or your class reunion in the year 2010 _ you might
want to start slimming down. Now. (Minor, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
