   With
</P>
<P>
   TURKEY-CENTER (Izmit, Turkey) _ The story from the city at the
center of the earthquake. There are incredible scenes of
destruction; the oil refinery is still burning and exploding. By
Edmund L. Andrews.
</P>
<P>
   And
</P>
<P>
   TURKEY-SCENE (Dateline to kum) _ A second feature, details to be
determined, on the aftermath of the earthquake in northwest Turkey.
By Celestine Bohlen.
