</P>
<P>
   HOUTKIN-DAY-TRADING (Undated) _ Harvey Houtkin, chief executive
officer of All-Tech Investment Group, one of the nation's largest
day-trading firms, fervently believes that securities regulators
are out to get him. But he also has absolutely no doubt that he
will go down in history as a man who made Wall Street a better
place for the small investor. By Gretchen Morgenson.
