<P>
   BAYOU _ GALLIANO, La. _ Georgia Tech's two new basketball
recruits come from the same ultra-wealthy household down the
Louisiana bayou. Though Clarence Moore is black and Ross Chouest
white, they consider themselves brothers. They created a little
basketball dynasty in this football-crazy area, and their great
fortune continued when Tech offered both a scholarship. Chouest has
lived a golden-spoon existence since birth, while Moore has
undergone major family hardships before Ross' parents became his
legal guardian. (Tierney, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). WITH
PHOTOS.
