   _ KKSF music director  &UR; Blake Lawrence &LR;  is hiding under his desk,
having received word, from GTSO Records, that  &UR; John Tesh &LR; 's version
of  &UR; Ricky Martin &LR; 's ``Livin' La Vida Loca'' is coming.
