<DOCNO> NYT19990818.0261 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-18 18:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2010 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w BC-POLITICS-DROPOUTS-1ST     08-18 1006
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-POLITICS-DROPOUTS-1STLD-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;    
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    FOR PRESIDENTIAL CANDIDATES WHO CRASH AND BURN, DEFEAT IS
FLEETING
 &HT;    EDS: Corrects spelling of Linda DiVall in last two grafs.
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (p) politics categories.
 &HT;    By SCOTT SHEPARD
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
