<HEADLINE>
TEEN DRUG USE IS DOWN, US SAYS 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (w and a coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By EUN LEE KOH  
 c.1999 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ Teen drug use dropped last year, but use among
young adults continued to increase, signaling worrisome trends for
the group, the government announced Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
   Health officials, releasing the annual National Household Survey
on Drug Abuse, reported that the rate of drug use among the general
