percent.
</P>
<P>
   ``The message is finally getting through,'' Shalala said. ``But
we have a long way to go because more than a million young people
are dependent on drugs. ...That's a million too many.''
</P>
<P>
   According to the survey, marijuana draws nearly twice as many
