outdoor sports but could soon become boxing's mecca for training.
Fighters from South Africa, New Zealand, Mexico and Poland, even
less exotic locales like Oxnard, New York and Detroit, flock to
this mountain hideaway to prepare their bodies and minds for the
ring. 
